		                    										<h2><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/healthcare-network/2012/jan/17/nhs-family-and-friend-recommendations">Why the NHS needs a friends and family test</a></h2>
											                    	
		                    	
		                    	
		                    		            		                    
		                    	
		                    	
		                    																			<p>If patients don't answer 'yes' when you ask them if they would recommend the hospital to family and friends then you know you've got a problem, says <strong>Stephen Dunn</strong></p>
		                    	
		                    	
		                    		            		                    
		                    	
		                    	
		                    	
		                    																			 	
																																									                	    





		
										

        		
		
			            						
										
					
